## 3. Solution Architecture

### 3.1 Plugin Dependency Declaration

Each plugin declares its input requirements:

```python
class EffectPlugin:
    @property
    def required_inputs(self) -> Set[str]:
        """Declare what inputs this plugin needs."""
        needs = set()
        if self.needs_depth:
            needs.add("depth")
        if self.needs_audio:
            needs.add("audio")
        if self.needs_midi:
            needs.add("midi")
        if self.needs_osc:
            needs.add("osc")
        if self.needs_background:
            needs.add("background")
        return needs
    
    @property
    def provides(self) -> Set[str]:
        """Declare what outputs this plugin produces."""
        provides = set()
        if self.produces_depth:
            provides.add("depth")
        if self.produces_audio_modulated:
            provides.add("audio_modulated")
        # ...
        return provides
```

