## 9. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Scheduler incorrectly batches plugins | High | Comprehensive testing; visual dependency graph debugger |
| Cycle detection misses edge cases | Medium | Use proven Kahn's algorithm; unit tests for cycles |
| Error wrapper hides bugs | Medium | Log full tracebacks; error count visible in UI |
| Parallel execution causes GL issues | High | Start with sequential; add threading only after thorough testing |
| Performance overhead exceeds budget | High | Pre-compute schedule; cache aggressively; Cython optimization |
| Migration of 80+ plugins error-prone | Medium | Automated migration script; manual review checklist |

